GIRARDI KEESE LAW FIRM, petitioner,
v.
PLAINTIFF ADVISORY COMMITTEE, et al. No. 15-704. Supreme Court of the United States Feb. 29, 2016.

*1168Motion of Vicente Ruiz, et al. for leave to file a brief as amici curiae granted. Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Third Circuit denied.
